      <section class='column'>
              <div class="sole-header headline-2 widgets-jobs-teaser__headline">
    Arbeitgeber stellen sich vor
  </div>

<div class="tiles">
  <div class="row tiles__row">
      <div class="small-12 medium-6 large-3 columns tiles__columns">
          <a class="tile" href="/arbeitgeber/saarbruecken-graduate-school-of-computer-science">
            <div class="tile__figure">
                <img srcset="https://bilder.academics.de/logo_su_gsocs.png?auto=format&amp;h=90&amp;w=216 216w, https://bilder.academics.de/logo_su_gsocs.png?auto=format&amp;h=180&amp;w=432 432w, https://bilder.academics.de/logo_su_gsocs.png?auto=format&amp;h=90&amp;w=216 216w, https://bilder.academics.de/logo_su_gsocs.png?auto=format&amp;h=180&amp;w=432 432w, https://bilder.academics.de/logo_su_gsocs.png?auto=format&amp;h=90&amp;w=216 216w, https://bilder.academics.de/logo_su_gsocs.png?auto=format&amp;h=180&amp;w=432 432w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 216px, (max-width: 1023px) 216px, 216px" class="tile__image tile__image--fit" alt="Saarland University GSoCS - Logo" src="https://bilder.academics.de/logo_su_gsocs.png?auto=format&amp;h=90&amp;w=216" />
            </div>
            <div class="headline-6-light tile__headline-6-light">
              From your Bachelor directly into our PhD Program!
            </div>
            <p>
              SaarbrÃ¼cken is your place to be if you are looking for one of the best places internationally to pursue a PhD in Computer Science.
            </p>
